data.description: Looking for the perfect farmhouse. situated on over an acre? Look no further. This one year old home features brand new LVP flooring throughout the main living areas. New carpet in all the bedrooms and closets. Huge kitchen with island that flows directly into a large family room. A built in butler's pantry featuring a large dining room perfect for your family gatherings. Master bedroom on the main level with a new bathroom remodel, new flooring, new tile and a upgraded shower. Large master closet. Upstairs you have three bedrooms and a large media room set up to add future doors. This home has so many upgraded features and is a must see! Please request Seller's disclosure for all the added features.
